Date: Mon, 11 Aug 2025 11:42:39 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 14/20] lib: add libvlc_downloader API

Used to download a file readable by VLC over a limited
set of protocols: http(s), ftp, file, nfs, smb, sftp

Refs #27971
